'Guide to Small Basic, Example 23-1
GraphicsWindow.Show()
GraphicsWindow.Title = "Example 23-1"
GraphicsWindow.Show()
GraphicsWindow.Width = 600
GraphicsWindow.Height = 400
GetPhoto:
Photo = Flickr.GetPictureOfMoment()
GraphicsWindow.DrawResizedImage(Photo, 0, 0, 600, 400)
Program.Delay(5000)
Goto GetPhoto
